<table border="0" height="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="1007" style="background:url(images/bg1.jpg)" align="center">
<!-- fwtable fwsrc="未命名" fwbase="sr.jpg" fwstyle="Dreamweaver" fwdocid = "1344182167" fwnested="1" -->
  <tr><!-- row 1 -->
    <td align="right" valign="top">
    
		<!--标题开始-->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:18pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	钟离权点石成金
	      </div>
	      <!-- 副标题 -->
	      <div style="font-family:'华文行楷'; font-size:16pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center; padding-top:15px;">
	      	
	      </div>
	      <!--标题结束-->
		<div style="text-align:center"><a name="1" id="1"></a>
		<img name="sr_r3_c1" src="images/sr_r3_c1.gif" width="293" height="32" border="0" id="sr_r3_c1" alt="" /></div>
		<!--图片-->
		
		<!--图片结束-->
		<!-- 作者 -->
		
			<div style="font-family:'宋体'; font-size:12pt;  color:#411500; text-align:center;padding-bottom:8px;">
		      	
		    </div>
		
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
	   		<!-- 显示内容 -->
	   		<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: center; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">陈雄群改编</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">钟离权收吕纯阳为徒，已经整整三年。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">这一天，师徒二人外出云游，路过一座大山，山势很陡，好像利剑刺向天空。骄阳照射着苍绿的峭壁。钟离权走在前面，步履轻盈，如履平地；吕纯阳跟在后面，一步一挪往上攀登。他肩上负着一个大包裹，足足有几十斤重，压得他呼哧呼哧地喘不过气来，额头上那豆大的汗珠不住地往外流，接着就卟哒卟哒地甩落在地上。肩上那个大包裹，是他师父钟离权在三年前交与他的，用锦帛包了一层又一层，沉甸甸的，不知包的是何物。可能是什么宝物，师父没对他说，他也不便询问，从师父交给他那天起，不管走到哪里，都要把它背上，一直背到如今。几天以前，肩膀就开始有些痛，他没有理会；昨天痛得更厉害了，他偷偷脱下衣服一瞧，原来肩膀已被压肿，磨破了皮，露出鲜红的嫩肉。他没吭声，今天又忍着痛，背上大包裹上山。这时，骄阳似火一般从头顶上直射下来，肩上的包裹更觉沉重，膀子上热辣辣的，像针扎一样的疼痛难忍。他只得不时背过手去，用手掌托起那个沉甸甸的大包裹，以减轻一点肩上的负担。这样一来，脚步自然就放慢了。但他并没有松劲，而是咬紧牙关，促使自己加快脚步，去追师父，不至于把距离拉得太大。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">钟离权上到山顶上以后，便回过头来看看，见吕洞宾还在半山腰里，艰难地往上爬。看到他那刚强的意志和持久的毅力，心里甚是喜悦，便在一棵大松树下坐卜来等他。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">过了片刻，吕纯阳终于登上山顶。钟离权笑盈盈地招呼他道：&ldquo;烈口当空，松下好乘凉，歇息一会儿再走吧!&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">吕纯阳正想歇息，便蹲下身来，把肩上的包裹卸下；不料，包裹没有放稳，竟咕噜噜滚下了山坡。吕纯阳心中甚是着急，唯恐损坏了师父的宝物，未等钟离权开口，便急忙奔下坡去捡拾。待到山坡下一看，当包裹用的锦帛，已被山石树茬划破，里面的东西已经暴露出来。吕纯阳一见，不禁大吃一惊。原来里面包的并不是什么贵重物件，更不是宝物，而是一块大顽石。吕纯阳呆呆地站在那里，看了许久，百思不得其解：&ldquo;师父要这么一块顽石有何用呢?&rdquo;他真想弃石而去；又一想，师父把它交与自己已经整整三年了。三年来，不管跋山涉水，还是严冬酷暑，这块顽石，从未离开过自己；师父也没说把它弃掉。既然背到了如今，师父又未发话，准有它的用场。这么一想，又重新把它包好，背上了山顶。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">钟离权站在山顶，早把吕纯阳的心思和行动看了个一清二楚。待他把顽石背上山顶后，便指着包裹道:&ldquo;现在可以把它打开!&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">吕纯阳解开包裹，顽石重新露了出来。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">钟离权笑呵呵地说道：&ldquo;你原来没想到这里面包的是一块顽石吧?&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">吕纯阳点了点头，不禁问道:&ldquo;不知师父要此顽石何用?&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">钟离权笑答道:&ldquo;一是用它磨炼尔之意志，二可将它点化成金。我即点石成金，也不枉你背它三年。&rdquo;说毕，用手指着那块大石头，说了一声&ldquo;变!&rdquo;那顽石立即变成了金光灿灿的一大块黄金。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">吕纯阳看得出神，连声赞叹道:&ldquo;师父竟有如此仙术，妙哉，妙哉!&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">钟离权言道:&ldquo;我将此点石成金之法传授与你如何?&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">吕纯阳沉吟了一会儿问道:&ldquo;化石为金，可保永无更变否?&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">钟离权回答说:&ldquo;所点之金，与真金不同，真金始终如一；所点之金，五百年后，仍变为石也。&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">吕纯阳听他这么一说，便拒绝学习这一法术，他说:&ldquo;若是如此，则弟子不愿学。&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">钟离权不解地问：&ldquo;为何不学?&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">吕纯阳接着说道:&ldquo;如此法术，兴利于五百年前，遗害于五百年后，岂不误了五百年后之人?故不愿学也。&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">钟离权听至此，不禁叹道:&ldquo;子之道念，我不及也，尔之正果当在我之上!&rdquo;</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-TOP: 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; MARGIN-BOTTOM: 0pt; TEXT-AUTOSPACE: ideograph-numeric" class="p0"><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'">从此，师徒相互切磋道义，进入更高境界。</span><span style="FONT-FAMILY: &quot;宋体&quot;; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-spacerun: 'yes'"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<!--EndFragment-->
	   </div>
	   <div style="text-align:left; color:#88510c; font-size:14px; line-height:20px; width:900px; height:auto; margin:0 auto;">
